Dean Paul Martin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dean_Paul_Martin 0 Dean Paul Martin Jr. (November 17, 1951 – March 21, 1987) was an American pop singer and film and television actor. A member of the California Air National Guard, Martin died in a crash during a military flight. Martin was the son of American entertainer Dean Martin.
